{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/7520", "repo": "rails", "body": "I agree with the rest of the comments here that this is outside the responsibility of AR, and probably outside the responsibility of Rails in general. \n\nAs a pattern, I feel that @evanphx's concept of having the decorator be in charge (instead of the finder) is cleaner and more appropriate. The fact that Evan's would work across ORM's is probably a signal of this.", "_id": {"$oid": "5237fac1bd3543c15100b6b9"}, "issue_id": 7520, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/8391469", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7520#issuecomment-8391469", "updated_at": "2012-09-08T17:05:04Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville", "login": "jredville", "gravatar_id": "6e0a92aa779bf439fe972b2b9b46a289", "html_url": "https://github.com/jredville", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/6e0a92aa779bf439fe972b2b9b46a289?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2Fba2fd310dcaa8781a9a652a31baf3c68.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 524, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/jredville/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2012-09-08T17:05:04Z", "id": 8391469, "owner": "rails"}
